Package om.tnavigator

Interface Summary
LogProcessorHandler Implemented by code that uses LogProcessor to process each log entry in turn.
TestLeaf This is the interface used by the navigation panel to get the information it needs to display each actual thing in the test (questions or text pages) in the appropriate state, and with a section heading before each section.
 

Class Summary
Log Facility for creating log files.
Log.LogFile Data about a single log file.
LogInputStream Input stream used for reading logs from a file that makes .log files into valid XML.
LogProcessor Use this in conjunction with something implementing LogProcessorHandler to carry out tasks that require looping around every log entry.
Mail Utilities for sending email.
NavigatorConfig Loads navigator configuration file.
NavigatorConfig.ExtraDatabase Additional database details
NavigatorServlet Om test navigator; implementation of the test delivery engine.
NavigatorServlet.QuestionVersion Class for storing a question version number.
NavigatorServlet.RequestTimings Class for accumulating performance information.
ShutdownManager Allows classes to be notified when the webapp is shut down so that they can null any relevant static member fields that might be keeping things from being properly GCed.
TestDefinition Represents the test definition XML file
TestDeployment Represents information from the .deploy.xml file
TestRealisation This class stores the structure of a test, as realised for a particular user.
UserSession Data stored about particular user
